{"tid":651934,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貴絶屯門】御半山折實15248元首推118伙","createTime":"2018-05-03T13:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T17:37:58.000Z","uid":68476,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe189d31657c3ea27e21c7e0f6990d4b5dcc956","tid":651934,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"【貴絶屯門】御半山折實15248元首推118伙<br />\n<br />\n昨日已預告今日開價、新地（0016）旗下屯門景秀里新盤御半山，今日公佈首張價單，首批涉118伙，平均實呎19302元，扣除最高21%直減折扣後，整批折實平均實呎15248元，不但較屯門景峰區一帶二手呎價高約3成，更貴絶屯門新盤。<br />\n<br />\n御半山首批118伙，定價由631.34萬元至924.48萬元，發展商提供最高21%折扣優惠（包括付款計劃優惠5%、置業售價折扣8%、特別折扣7%及新地會會員售價折扣優惠1%），折實價由498.75萬元至730.33萬元，折實實呎13740元至17026元。<br />\n<br />\n入場單位為1A室1樓B室，屬實用304方呎一房戶，定價631.34萬元，折實價498.75萬元，折實實呎16406元。<br />\n<br />\n新地代理業務部總經理張卓秀敏形容，首批為「萬眾期待開心價」，與同區二手屋苑價錢比較屬合理，折實價500萬以下單位有3伙，本周六起收票及開放示範單位予公眾，最快下周開售，首批折實市值約7.32億元，有機會開售前會再加推。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180503/s00003/79813c3104fda53707e69dd0dde80988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180503%2Fs00003%2F79813c3104fda53707e69dd0dde80988.jpg&h=8922ae87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6366725fd76d3e7cf74af1cb2f354f3c8dba6ec","tid":651934,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"屌奶星，屯門都成萬九蚊一呎"},{"pid":"c3bfde8d0ae1251c79aac9c4c4bbf0dd12b954f0","tid":651934,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"咁平，升多一倍先算合理"},{"pid":"d0c04395da6f7f1eb0ec885d23a6b4eaaf946e7a","tid":651934,"uid":142397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef102c94015f6043d140feecd980efa8746b6105","tid":651934,"uid":142397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"屎已食"}]}